  <h1>Privacy Policy - FairSplitly</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> November 2025</p>

  <p>FairSplitly does not collect, store, or share any personal data. All expense information, names, and usage details remain on your device and are never transmitted to any server.</p>

  <h2>Data Collection</h2>
  <p>FairSplitly operates entirely offline. It does not use analytics, cloud storage, advertisements, or any third-party SDKs.</p>

  <h2>Accounts</h2>
  <p>No user accounts, logins, or authentication are required.</p>

  <h2>Purchases & Ads</h2>
  <p>FairSplitly is a one-time purchase app. No subscriptions. No ads.</p>

  <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>The app does not connect to third-party APIs or services.</p>

  <h2>Children’s Privacy</h2>
  <p>No data is collected from anyone, including children under 13.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have questions, contact: <strong>support@fairsplitly.app</strong></p>

